 released him. May 19, 2018 In "Sports" West Ham vs Wolves : Manuel Pellegrini slammed his West Ham flops for their "very bad" start to the season after the Chilean's struggling side crashed to a fourth successive Premier League defeat. September 1, 2018 In "Sports" West Ham United have appointed former Manchester City boss Manuel Pellegrini as their new manager on a three-year deal, the Premier League club announced on Tuesday. May 22, 2018 In "News"